Access Tests
Consider
SimpleWindow W("Testing", 20, 10);
RectangleShape R(W, 2, 2, Blue, 4, 3);
const RectangleShape S(W, 15, 10, Red, 5, 6);
Can we do the following?
color c = R.GetColor();
color d = S.GetColor();
color d = R.thisColor;
R.DetColor(Yellow);
S.SetColor(Black);

